          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1705676272360-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>sriracha </strong>with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 4 min or until the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>rendang-inspired lean beef mince curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1705676277894-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
