            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1705676286769-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>rendang-inspired lean beef mince curry </strong>over the<strong> cooked rice </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced chillies </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Serve the<strong> lettuce wedges</strong> to the side and drizzle over the <strong>satay dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
